OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA fine and
OL,6,Fdry evening with plenty of late
OL,7,Fsunshine. Overnight will stay dry with
OL,8,Ffurther clear skies. A warm night to
OL,9,Fcome, especially in the towns and
OL,10,Fcities.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTuesday:FAnother very warm day on
OL,13,FTuesday, although sunshine likely to
OL,14,Fbe more hazy than recently, with some
OL,15,Fpatchy cloud around at times.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
