OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,6,FRemaining very warm with plenty more
OL,7,Fsunshine, although an increasing risk
OL,8,Fof some showers and thunderstorms at
OL,9,Ftimes. Lighter winds than Monday and
OL,10,FTuesday adding to the warm feel.
